These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-5-1::.
House: wooden, townhouse
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, skydiving
The people use 2 different means of transport: taxi, train
2 different games are played: scrabble, billiard
1. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the right of the townhouse house##5
2. the person driving the train is the person playing billiard##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| House          | townhouse    | wooden |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | skydiving |
| Transport   | taxi    | train    |
| Game   | scrabble  | billiard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-5-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, baking
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, october
2 different games are played: billiard, monopoly
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, snowmobile
1. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
2. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the person playing monopoly##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Hobby          | filmmaking | baking   |
| Birthday   | october        | august     |
| Game           | billiard         | monopoly     |
| Transport     | bus         | snowmobile |

