.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-5-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: chess, puzzles
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, august
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, fantasy
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: handball, parkour
1. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##5
2. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the left of the person watching documentary movies##5
3. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Hobby         | puzzles      | chess    |
| Birthday           | october | august |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy       | documentary    |
| Sport     | handball    | parkour     |

