.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-5-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, orchid
There 2 different types of food: kiwi, garlic
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, pony
1. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the owner of the pony##5
2. the person who growszinnia is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |
| Beverage      | coffee  | 7up        |
| Flower         | orchid | zinnia |
| Food   | kiwi    | garlic    |
| Pet     | pony | hedgehog        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-5-5::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, house
2 different games are played: monopoly, backgammon
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, blend
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, surfing
1. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
2. the person who's sport is surfing is in an odd position##4
3. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the blend-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |
| Music-Genre          | gospel | house      |
| Game           | backgammon | monopoly |
| Cigar   | swisher  | blend   |
| Sport         | surfing   | cycling     |

